title: Stocks to Watch - What the Russia/Ukraine Crisis Means for the Markets
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Ben Levisohn discuss the impact of sanctions, the outlook for commodities prices and interest rates, and the week ahead in stocks.
